                </div>
                <p>PET fiber mesh – excellent mosquito protection. Aluminum frame. Simple installation with included adhesive tape or screws. Rolls up when not needed. Perfect for UK sash windows and Australian sliding windows.</p>
                <ul class="specs-list">
                    <li><span class="specs-icon">✅</span> Custom made to your exact measurements</li>
                    <li><span class="specs-icon">✅</span> No tools required for installation</li>
                    <li><span class="specs-icon">✅</span> UV‑resistant, rust‑proof materials</li>
                    <li><span class="specs-icon">✅</span> Ships worldwide from Foshan, China</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="product-actions">
                    <a href="#inquiry" class="btn">Get a Quote →</a>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/8613536600067" class="btn btn-outline">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 详细描述区块（可选） -->
        <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background: var(--gray-light); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius);">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Product Details</h3>
            <p>This retractable roll‑up screen is engineered for simplicity and durability. The high‑density PET mesh blocks mosquitoes, flies, and midges while maintaining natural airflow. The aluminium frame is available in any colour to match your existing windows. Installation takes minutes: simply attach the frame using the supplied adhesive tape or screws – no professional help needed.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.8rem;">All MBORMC screens are manufactured in our Foshan factory using 6063‑T5 aluminium. We offer global shipping with wooden crate packaging, and every order comes with a detailed DIY installation guide.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- 底部联系栏（与首页相同） -->
<div class="contact-bar">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="contact-links">
            <a href="https://wa.me/8613536600067" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📱 WhatsApp: +86 135 3660 0067</a>
            <a href="#" id="wechatCopyBtn" style="cursor: pointer;">💬 WeChat: FSMBOR (click to copy)</a>
            <span>📍 MBORMC Production Base, Dali Town, Nanhai District, Foshan, Guangdong, China</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 页脚（与首页相同） -->
<footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
        <p>© 2025 MBORMC® — DIY Insect Screen Manufacturer for UK & Australia</p>
        <p class="footer-address">Factory direct pricing · Worldwide shipping · 2-year DIY warranty</p>
        <p><a href="https://www.insectscreen.cc/">Home</a> | <a href="https://www.insectscreen.cc/#products">Products</a> | <a href="https://www.insectscreen.cc/#inquiry">Contact</a></p>
    </div>
</footer>

<script>
    // 移动端菜单（复用首页逻辑）
    const menuToggle = document.getElementById('mobileMenuBtn');
    const navList = document.getElementById('navLinks');
    if(menuToggle) {
        menuToggle.addEventListener('click', () => navList.classList.toggle('show'));
    }
    // 微信复制功能
    function copyWechat() {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText('FSMBOR').then(() => {
            alert('WeChat ID "FSMBOR" copied to clipboard');
        }).catch(() => {
            prompt('Press Ctrl+C to copy WeChat ID:', 'FSMBOR');
        });
    }
    const wechatBtn = document.getElementById('wechatCopyBtn');
    if(wechatBtn) wechatBtn.addEventListener('click', (e) => { e.preventDefault(); copyWechat(); });
    const wechatFloating = document.getElementById('wechatFloatingBtn');
    if(wechatFloating) wechatFloating.addEventListener('click', copyWechat);
</script>
</body>
</html>
